{"tid":216784,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"IELTS考試溫習一問","createTime":"2017-04-25T12:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T06:12:08.000Z","uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d38c811faf799edef6718324961ddef447a633a9","tid":216784,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:10:24.000Z","msg":"想問有無巴絲考前做過cambridge 10 11?<br />\n知唔知同實際考試難道相差幾遠？<br />\n<br />\n而家狂做listening同reading分數好飄忽，有啲7.5有啲6.5。而家做到好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外你地writing可以點practice?我writing好弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f8ae34e99a9d9bf02125885836c02b2a6f4ee3","tid":216784,"uid":64178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:19:50.000Z","msg":"報咗幾時"},{"pid":"3fb9c273369d6169fa09c79139355718d8d8e0c4","tid":216784,"uid":35837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我考個時同練習好唔同 佢2篇reading都係段落大意 <br />\n只可以講 練習始終都係練習<br />\n同真既考試唔同 唔好太著重練習個分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油"},{"pid":"a6eb16d37fa3f79ae0d8e44c0cc338c66aef9e42","tid":216784,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T17:58:16.000Z","msg":"認真唔使理練習分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做過份練習勁低分 去考過兩次都高過佢"},{"pid":"11bdcedda7d911240748b1a5f82eb8d12a1d8089","tid":216784,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報咗幾時</blockquote><br />\n我未報呀，覺得好似好多不足，我怕writing好低分。 <br />\n因為太耐無寫過啲formal 嘅內容，做咗野幾年啲writing skill真係忘記得一乾二淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989cef92fa3a886df94ecfebc41d1c403e277163","tid":216784,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真唔使理練習分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做過份練習勁低分 去考過兩次都高過佢</blockquote><br />\n你係點溫？做咩paper practice？差幾遠？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d761c549391da6262a8bca9f6f2b89e92d7adc","tid":216784,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報咗幾時</blockquote><br />\n我係咪應該報一次考定try try先？"},{"pid":"d498d7c0026c2f063fcf8edebf3df7586eec8c63","tid":216784,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:32:25.000Z","msg":"愈緊張愈差"},{"pid":"4ffe29fa96059e620569491cba6b0cd49aa04489","tid":216784,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真唔使理練習分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做過份練習勁低分 去考過兩次都高過佢</blockquote><br />\n你係點溫？做咩paper practice？差幾遠？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇點溫過 因為嗰排考梗DSE 但係睇左題型<br />\n我覺得佢出啲野內容比較似啲相對academic嘅雜誌嘅野<br />\n唔記得係咩mock 因為係朋友影印俾我嘅 淨係記得差最多嘅係reading 份mock話我6.5最後考過兩次 一次7.5一次8.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abfbdc9faa5c9f9bb2ecf8a53b3a89848b0424a","tid":216784,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>報咗幾時</blockquote><br />\n我係咪應該報一次考定try try先？</blockquote><br />\n可以啊 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52971009c4358990102cbe274caf2db53c524aab","tid":216784,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真唔使理練習分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做過份練習勁低分 去考過兩次都高過佢</blockquote><br />\n你係點溫？做咩paper practice？差幾遠？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇點溫過 因為嗰排考梗DSE 但係睇左題型<br />\n我覺得佢出啲野內容比較似啲相對academic嘅雜誌嘅野<br />\n唔記得係咩mock 因為係朋友影印俾我嘅 淨係記得差最多嘅係reading 份mock話我6.5最後考過兩次 一次7.5一次8.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我去報左先喇，我諗住去北歐報master<br />\n佢要求唔高要overall 6.5以上就ok。 <br />\n我怕fail的話要等多年先可以報所以咁緊張"},{"pid":"3f7127faa7cf014e4701e24882fbebc85681905a","tid":216784,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真唔使理練習分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做過份練習勁低分 去考過兩次都高過佢</blockquote><br />\n你係點溫？做咩paper practice？差幾遠？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇點溫過 因為嗰排考梗DSE 但係睇左題型<br />\n我覺得佢出啲野內容比較似啲相對academic嘅雜誌嘅野<br />\n唔記得係咩mock 因為係朋友影印俾我嘅 淨係記得差最多嘅係reading 份mock話我6.5最後考過兩次 一次7.5一次8.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我去報左先喇，我諗住去北歐報master<br />\n佢要求唔高要overall 6.5以上就ok。 <br />\n我怕fail的話要等多年先可以報所以咁緊張</blockquote><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf7f2da269ec8c708a40b889a5a3e45353bda20","tid":216784,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"用三個星期溫夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9128faba4a5c9df2a6fb17deb8214ed05486a4d5","tid":216784,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"冇做10 11 不過有做1-9<br />\n唔洗太緊張 我做果陣都係份份6.5-7.5 但考出黎reading 8 listening 8.5 <br />\nReading我自己就會睇左問題先 再睇文搵答案 睇文再睇題之後再係文到搵答案好曬時間 除非你可以速讀睇題目再仔細睇文都夠時間<br />\nListening 就要記著d s 諗d簡寫出黎 聽到答案寫簡寫落去 完錄音再寫個答案落去"},{"pid":"88bad38a6ad22e04963f6bbeb82c43e3709ea044","tid":216784,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"Cambridge 本野不嬲都難過正式IELTS好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\