ng 就要記著d s 諗d簡寫出黎 聽到答案寫簡寫落去 完錄音再寫個答案落去</blockquote><br />\n 唔該晒巴打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問你係咪做academic 定general?</blockquote><br />\nAcademic writing 都冇乜可以同你講 因為我都係得6<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}